          <p>Complete API reference with examples, authentication guides, and endpoint descriptions.</p>
          <span class="resource-link">View Docs →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/en/docs/sdk" class="resource-card animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="resource-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
              <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>SDK Downloads</h3>
          <p>Official SDKs for JavaScript, Python, and Ruby. Get started with pre-built client libraries.</p>
          <span class="resource-link">Download SDKs →</span>
